    "causal_summary": "deep-loop-workflows is the single public skill that merges active deep-loop persona modes (deep-research, deep-review, deep-ai-council, deep-improvement) into one advisor identity with active mode packets, routed by workflowMode through mode-registry.json over the frozen MCP-free deep-loop-runtime backend. @context owns one-shot retrieval while research and review carry bounded context snapshots. Per-mode convergence, state, artifacts, and tool-permission contracts are preserved unflattened; the three-tier discriminator (workflowMode / runtimeLoopType / backendKind) keeps graph-backed modes and improvement-host/external-adapter modes distinct.",
